<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">

  <%- include('../partials/head', {
    title: "Paginas Bellas || Registro"
}) %>
  <body>
    <%- include('../partials/header') %>
  <main class="register">
    <section class="register-box">
      <h2>Bienvenido</h2>
      <p>Lorem ipsum dolor, sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Nam exercitationem expedita ratione, nemo quas fuga a nihil ut vel perspiciatis natus, distinctio architecto repudiandae porro voluptatibus neque optio qui tempore.
      </p>
      <article class="register-form">
        <form method="POST" action="" class="register-form-info">
          <div class="register-info">
            <input class="<%= locals.errors && errors.nombre ? 'Es invalid' : null %>" type="text" id="nombre" name="nombre" placeholder="Escribi tu nombre" value="<%= locals.old && old.nombre ? old.nombre : null%>">
            <span><%= locals.errors && errors.nombre ? errors.nombre.msg : null%></span>
          </div>
          <div class="register-info">
            <input class="<%= locals.errors && errors.apellido ? 'Es invalid' : null %>" type="text" id="apellido" name="apellido" placeholder="Escribi tu apellido" value="<%= locals.old && old.apellido ? old.apellido : null%>">
            <label for="apellido"></label>
            <span><%= locals.errors && errors.apellido ? errors.apellido.msg : null%></span>
          </div>
          <div class="register-info">
            <input class="<%= locals.errors && errors.email ? 'Is invalid' : null %>" type="email" id="email" name="email" placeholder="Email" value="<%= locals.old && old.email ? old.email : null%>">
            <label for="email"></label>
            <span><%= locals.errors && errors.email ? errors.email.msg : null%></span>
          </div>
          <div class="register-info">
            <input class="<%= locals.errors && errors.password ? 'Is invalid' : null %>" type="password" id="password" name="password" placeholder="Contraseña">
            <label for="password"></label>
            <span><%= locals.errors && errors.password ? errors.password.msg : null%></span>
          </div>
          <div class="register-info">
            <input class="<%= locals.errors && errors.password2 ? 'Is invalid' : null %>" type="password" id="password" name="password2" placeholder="Repeti la contraseña">
            <label for="password"></label>
            <span><%= locals.errors && errors.password2 ? errors.password.msg : null%></span>
          </div>
          <div class="register-condiciones">
            <input type="checkbox" name="terminos" id="terminos">
            <label for="terminos">Aceptar <a href="">Terminos y Condiciones</a></label>
            <span><%= locals.errors && errors.terminos ? errors.terminos.msg : null%></span>
          </div>
          <div class="register-boton-box">
            <button class="register-button" type="submit">Registrarme</button>
            <button class="register-button" type="reset"> <a href="/">Cancelar</a></button>
          </div>

          <div class="register-info">
            <p>O puedes registrarte con:</p>
            <div class="register-boton-box">
              <button class="register-boton-rojo"> <a href="https://accounts.google.com/signin/v2/identifier?continue=https%3A%2F%2Fmail.google.com%2Fmail%2F&service=mail&sacu=1&rip=1&flowName=GlifWebSignIn&flowEntry=ServiceLogin"><i class="fa-brands fa-google-plus"></i> Google </a></button>

              <button class="register-boton-azul"><a href="https://es-la.facebook.com/"><i class="fa-brands fa-facebook"></i> Facebook</a></button>
            </div>
          </div>
        </form>
      </article>
      <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Enim, suscipit iste esse provident laudantium fugit
        nostrum debitis sint inventore. Dicta placeat culpa velit consequuntur dolore ut sunt ex doloribus nulla!
        Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Blanditiis, accusantium tempore suscipit, hic iusto
        nisi quae facere cupiditate nemo distinctio explicabo sed reprehenderit. Delectus autem pariatur porro magnam,
        incidunt quidem.
      </p>
    </section>
  </main>
  <%- include('../partials/footer') %>   
</body>

</html>
